'''托马斯·查尔斯·波尔特'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Charles Poulter}}）是一名[[美国|美国]][[科学家|科学家]]和[[南极|南极]][[探险家|探险家]]，曾在[[伊利諾理工學院|阿芒技术研究所]]和[[国际斯坦福研究所|国际斯坦福研究所]]任副主任。<ref name = "Nielson">{{cite book | last = Nielson | first = Donald | title = A Heritage of Innovation: SRI's First Half Century | publisher = SRI International | year = 2006 | isbn = 978-0-9745208-1-0 | location = [[Menlo_Park,_California|Menlo Park, California]] | pages = 11–2–11–4}}</ref> 他在[[李察·柏德|李察·柏德]]導的第二次伯德南極特派團中獲得第二指揮權，[[波爾特冰川|波爾特冰川]]就是以他的名字命名。<ref name="OverTheYears">{{cite book|first=Thomas|last=Poulter|year=1977|title=Over the years|location=[[Menlo_Park,_California|Menlo Park, California]]|publisher=[[Stanford_Research_Institute|Stanford Research Institute]]}}</ref><ref name="IntoLittleAmerica">Into Little America documentary film (1935)</ref>

